      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to drive home an absolute dream? This car is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, and it\u2019s been kept in tip-top shape with zero compromises. It drives incredibly smooth and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how perfect it is. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
