    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 power unit, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS system. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, while the chassis remains structurally perfect with documented subframe reinforcement. Mechanically flawless, the suspension retains its factory-fresh damping characteristics, and the M-Variable limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution. A true purist\u2019s spec, maintained with obsessive attention to mechanical integrity and performance metrics.",
