    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, presenting in breathtaking showroom condition as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; the factory paint remains vibrant and consistent across every meticulously aligned panel. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury, with the premium hand-stitched leather still retaining its original matte texture and that distinct, clean aroma of a new vehicle. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the intuitive touch-interface navigation, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of maintenance records included to prove its history. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been exposed to inclement weather or harsh road conditions. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a flawlessly preserved example of automotive excellence.",
